import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; function App() { const[apidata,setapidata]=useState(null); const[weath,setweather]=useState(); const[city,setcity]=useState("Mumbai"); const addaction= async()=>{ let url=`https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather?q=${city}&units=metric&appid=7f40a7595102633b575991d81ac826cd` const res = await fetch(url); const data = await res.json(); console.log(data); setapidata(data.main); setweather(data.weather); } useEffect(()=>{addaction();},[city]); return ( <>
{setcity(e.target.value)}} />
